description:
Diabetic Living India - April 2014  IN

100 Pages | True PDF | English | 24 MB 


Diabetic Living focuses on improving the quality of life for those affected by diabetes, and addresses a variety of health concerns for readers of all ages. Each issue offers lifestyle-focused content including information on the latest medical breakthroughs, health care, effective exercise ideas, nutrition tips, healthy eating choices, easy diabetic recipes, diabetic product and brand recommendations. Diabetic Living provides solutions for the many facets of self care for people with diabetes.
